1
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,840
His grandpa,

2
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:20,880
Xiyan,

3
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,520
Zhen,

4
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,560
did you all see this?

5
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:31,000
I finally lived to see our Dong

6
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:34,640
grow up and get married.

7
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,759
I have finally fulfilled

8
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:41,320
my duty to you.

9
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:45,840
It was all worth it.

10
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,680
Right?

11
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,960
Listen to me.

12
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,840
From up in heaven,

13
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,800
you must bless

14
00:01:56,960 --> 00:02:01,080
our children to be safe and sound.

15
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:04,520
Please bless A Dong and his wife

16
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:08,160
with a happy life.

17
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,760
And bless A Dong

18
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:14,640
with many children

19
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:19,079
and grandchildren.

20
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,760
A Liang.

21
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:30,480
I really miss you.

22
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,280
If you are still alive,

23
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:38,640
come back quickly

24
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,800
and reunite with your wife.

25
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:45,200
It's just too hard for your wife

26
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:49,560
to be all alone.

27
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:56,120
If you are no longer in this world,

28
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:00,480
visit me in a dream

29
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,120
and let me know.

30
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,560
Just watch over

31
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:09,960
your wife,

32
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:13,440
your brother and his wife,

33
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,440
and keep them safe.

34
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,680
My dear.

35
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,960
Wait for me.

36
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:43,600
I'm coming to join you.

37
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,480
Peace.

38
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,240
Have a smooth life,

39
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,600
have many children,

40
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,480
and prosper.

41
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,360
Grandma,

42
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,120
Jiadong and Wangshu

43
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,520
are here to kowtow to you.

44
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,200
Grandma.

45
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,880
Grandma.

46
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:29,520
Grandma.

47
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,280
Grandma.

48
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,640
Grandma.

49
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,560
Grandma.

50
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,159
Grandma has passed away.

51
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,560
Grandma.

52
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,400
Grandma.

53
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:56,680
Grandma.

54
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,159
Didn't you want to see

55
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,120
Wangshu and me

56
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,680
have a child?

57
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,680
Didn't you want to see

58
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,880
your great-grandson

59
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,720
grow up day by day,

60
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,520
see the Japanese get driven away,

61
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,360
and see our days get

62
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,360
better day by day?

63
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,280
Grandma.

64
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,920
Grandma, wake up.

65
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,440
Don't leave me.

66
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,640
Grandma will see.

67
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,600
She, Mom, and Dad

68
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,130
will all be watching us.

69
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,600
Grandma.

70
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:39,960
Grandma.

71
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,840
I am unfilial.

72
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:45,080
I should be at home mourning for you.

73
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,120
But these 15 overseas letters

74
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,720
haven't been delivered yet.

75
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,920
After Wangshu and I

76
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,760
finish delivering these letters,

77
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:53,080
we will come back to kowtow

78
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,080
and mourn for you.

79
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,560
Jiadong,

80
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,280
this is also Grandma's wish.

81
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,080
I think

82
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,400
she will definitely understand us.

83
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:16,960
Let's go.

84
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,600
Wangshu, Jiadong,

85
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,240
follow me.

86
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,240
Song Zhi.

87
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,840
This is

88
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,480
the dowry I prepared for you.

89
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,680
These are

90
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,960
all the belongings your Grandpa

91
00:06:57,960 --> 00:07:00,600
left behind.

92
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,640
Tell Adong,

93
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,800
the Chen family

94
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:15,280
has a clear conscience.

95
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,280
Our backbones

96
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,960
are straight.

97
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:30,440
He must be

98
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,960
an upright person.

99
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,520
Grandma.

100
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,810
Sister-in-law.

101
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:45,520
I remembered everything Grandma said.

102
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,320
I definitely won't bring shame to her

103
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,920
and the Chen ancestors.

104
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,530
Sister-in-law.

105
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,730
Are you really not considering getting married?

106
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,600
What?

107
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,330
Are you driving me away too?

108
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,480
Of course not.

109
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,610
Sister-in-law.

110
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,370
Just like Grandma said,

111
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,760
you're not just our sister-in-law.

112
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,600
You also raised Jiadong

113
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,000
just like

114
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,320
his mother.

115
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:15,260
No matter what decision you make,

116
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,960
you're always our sister-in-law.

117
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:17,880
We're family.

118
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,040
Okay.

119
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,440
Then you keep these.

120
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,040
From now on,

121
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,410
you are the head of this family.

122
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,490
Sister-in-law,

123
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,419
I don't know anything about this.

124
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,010
Jiadong and I are going out.

125
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,480
So we might have to trouble you

126
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,760
to help manage these.

127
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,080
But this

128
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,600
was left to you by Grandma,

129
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,340
so you must keep it safe yourself.

130
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,610
Sister-in-law,

131
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,090
just listen to Wangshu.

132
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,640
By the way, sister-in-law,

133
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,680
I heard from Brother Mingshu that

134
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,560
the anti-Japanese organizations are killing enemies

135
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,480
and are currently short of food and weapons.

136
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,010
Wangshu and I discussed it,

137
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,760
and we want to do our part too.

138
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,930
So I was thinking

139
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,560
of taking half of these

140
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,160
and donating them to the anti-Japanese organization.

141
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,280
Is that okay with you?

142
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:10,920
But

143
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,440
these are our family's

144
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,440
last belongings.

145
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,570
With the world so chaotic outside,

146
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,520
we don't even know how we'll survive

147
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,360
in the future.

148
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,520
Besides,

149
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,930
you and Wangshu will have children in the future,

150
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,000
so we must leave a way out

151
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,200
for ourselves.

152
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,010
Sister-in-law,

153
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:31,080
no egg stays unbroken when the nest is overturned.

154
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,880
Only when the invaders are driven back

155
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,080
and the country is at peace,

156
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,040
can our small family

157
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,280
have peaceful days.

158
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,040
Yes, sister-in-law.

159
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,340
I support Jiadong.

160
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,320
The soldiers on the frontline

161
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:44,240
are risking their lives, leaving their families and homes behind.

162
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,300
We can't just think about ourselves.

163
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,680
Alright,

164
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,370
I'll listen to you both.

165
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,120
I don't understand those big principles

166
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,380
you are talking about.

167
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,490
This will count as mine.

168
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,730
As your sister-in-law,

169
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,400
I can't hold you back.

170
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,720
Thank you, sister-in-law.

171
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,480
Thank you, sister-in-law.
